1. On je izjavio da će učiniti sve po svojim *imenom*. (He declared to do all in his name.)
2. Deca su zvala majku *imenom*. (The children called their mother by name.)
3. On je napravio izjavu *imenom* firme. (He made a statement in the name of the company.)
4. Ona je govorila *imenom* svog sinu. (She spoke in the name of her son.)
5. Oni su se predstavili *imenom* svojih roditelja. (They presented themselves by the name of their parents.)